
This directory contains example scripts demonstrating how to use the FLTK
Perl module. Here is a quick summary of what each example is:

  hello.pl      - The ubiquitous Hello World.
  boxtypes.pl   - The boxtypes demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  browser.pl    - The browser demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  buttons.pl    - The buttons demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  fonts.pl      - Simple example demonstrating font usage.
  input.pl      - The input demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  label.pl      - The label demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  menu.pl       - Very short example of a menu.
  pack.pl       - The pack demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  radio.pl      - The radio demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  tabs.pl       - The tabs demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  tile.pl       - The tile demo from FLTK redone in Perl.
  viewer.pl     - A simple Text Editor demo that syntax highlights Perl code.

